OL,5, Some of Wall Street biggest companies  
OL,6, have been fined a total of $1.8bn      
OL,7, (#1.7bn) by US financial watchdogs     
OL,8, after staff discussed deals and trades 
OL,9, on their personal devices and apps.    
OL,11,FThe Securities and Exchange Commission 
OL,12,F(SEC) says the investigation uncovered 
OL,13,F"pervasive off-channel communications".
OL,15,FBarclays, UBS and Goldman Sachs were   
OL,16,Famong the 16 firms named by regulators.
OL,18,FThe sweeping industry probe is a       
OL,19,Flandmark case for the SEC and Commodity
OL,20,FFutures Trading Commission (CFTC).     
